          <h1>VPN for Streaming: Beat Geo-Blocks & Stream Smoothly (2026)</h1>

          <p class="note">
            <strong>Quick answer:</strong>
            A VPN can help you access geo-restricted catalogs and protect your traffic on public Wi-Fi — but it must be configured correctly (DNS/IPv6/WebRTC leak-safe) and you’ll often need the right server type for each platform.
          </p>

