          <p style="margin:14px 0 0; color:#000; font-weight:800;">
            Speed tip: choose a <a href="/en-us/blog/which-vpn-server.html">nearby server</a> first, then change region only if you need a specific catalog.
            For deeper tuning see <a href="/en-us/blog/vpn-optimal-settings.html">VPN optimal settings</a> and <a href="/en-us/blog/vpn-protocols.html">VPN protocols</a>.
          </p>
