            For geo-restrictions specifically, see <a href="/en-us/blog/vpn-geo-blocks.html">VPN geo-blocks</a>.
            For account-sensitive scenarios (banking), see <a href="/en-us/blog/vpn-banking-online.html">VPN and online banking</a>.
          </p>
